Version 0.0.13
* Fixed build with boost 1.88 (bsc#1242801)

Version 0.0.12
* Added selinux-policy and systemd-boot to hard reboot list.

Version 0.0.11
* Handle content-length of stomp in zypper plugin

Version 0.0.10
* Updated zypp-boot-plugin.conf docu.

Version 0.0.9
* Set reboot flag for multiversion packages ( type "M" ).

Version 0.0.8
* Do not overwrite higher bootlevel in already existing reboot-needed.

Version 0.0.7
* Caching RPM calls for speedup.

Version 0.0.6
* Using Boost:child for RPM calls instead of unsecure system()
  call (bsc#1215988).

Version 0.0.5
* Fix in checking installhint(reboot-needed) (bsc#1215988).

Version 0.0.4
* Added libopenssl to soft-reboot, removed openssl from soft-reboot

Version 0.0.3
* Allowing regex expression for the package name in zypp-boot-plugin.conf.

Version 0.0.2
* Reduced logging in order not to overload the communication with libzypp.

Version 0.0.1
* Initial release
